  "id": "api/core/defineInjectable",
  "title": "defineInjectable",
  "contents": "\n\n<article>\n  <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/edit/master/packages/core/src/di/defs.ts?message=docs(core)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...#L111-L136\" aria-label=\"Suggest Edits\" title=\"Suggest Edits\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/7.0.0/packages/core/src/di/defs.ts#L111-L136\" aria-label=\"View Source\" title=\"View Source\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n    <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n      {\n        \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n        \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n        \"itemListElement\": [\n          { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io//api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n          { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/core\", \"name\": \"@angular/core\" } },\n          { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/core/defineInjectable\", \"name\": \"defineInjectable\" } }\n        ]\n      }\n    </script>\n      <a href=\"/api\">API</a> > <a href=\"api/core\">@angular/core</a>\n  </div>\n  \n  <header class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"defineinjectable\">defineInjectable<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/defineInjectable#defineinjectable\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label function\">function</label>\n    \n    \n    \n  </header>\n  \n  <aio-toc class=\"embedded\"></aio-toc>\n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n    \n  <section class=\"short-description\">\n    <p>Construct an <code>InjectableDef</code> which defines how a token will be constructed by the DI system, and\nin which injectors (if any) it will be available.</p>\n\n    <p><a href=\"api/core/defineInjectable#description\">See more...</a></p>\n  </section>\n  \n  \n  \n\n  \n\n<code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" linenums=\"false\" class=\"no-box api-heading\"> <span class=\"member-name\"><a href=\"api/core/defineInjectable\" class=\"code-anchor\">defineInjectable</a></span>&#x3C;T>(opts: {\n    <a href=\"api/core/Injectable#providedIn\" class=\"code-anchor\">providedIn</a>?: <a href=\"api/core/Type\" class=\"code-anchor\">Type</a>&#x3C;any> | 'root' | 'any' | null;\n    <a href=\"api/core/ResolvedReflectiveFactory#factory\" class=\"code-anchor\">factory</a>: () => T;\n}): never</code-example>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"parameters\">Parameters</h4>\n<table class=\"is-full-width list-table parameters-table function-overload-parameters\">\n  <tbody>\n  \n    <tr class=\"function-overload-parameter\">\n      <td class=\"param-name\"><a id=\"\"></a>opts</td>\n      \n      <td class=\"param-description\">\n            <p>Type: <code>{\n    <a href=\"api/core/Injectable#providedIn\" class=\"code-anchor\">providedIn</a>?: <a href=\"api/core/Type\" class=\"code-anchor\">Type</a><any> | 'root' | 'any' | null;\n    factory: () => T;\n}</any></code>.</p>\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n\n\n<h4 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"returns\">Returns</h4>\n<p><code>never</code></p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n  \n\n  \n\n<section class=\"description\">\n  <h2 id=\"description\">Description<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/defineInjectable#description\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <p>This should be assigned to a static <code>ngInjectableDef</code> field on a type, which will then be an\n<code><a href=\"api/core/InjectableType\" class=\"code-anchor\">InjectableType</a></code>.</p>\n<p>Options:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code><a href=\"api/core/Injectable#providedIn\" class=\"code-anchor\">providedIn</a></code> determines which injectors will include the injectable, by either associating it\nwith an <code>@<a href=\"api/core/NgModule\" class=\"code-anchor\">NgModule</a></code> or other <code><a href=\"api/core/InjectorType\" class=\"code-anchor\">InjectorType</a></code>, or by specifying that this injectable should be\nprovided in the <code>'root'</code> injector, which will be the application-level injector in most apps.</li>\n<li><code><a href=\"api/core/ResolvedReflectiveFactory#factory\" class=\"code-anchor\">factory</a></code> gives the zero argument function which will create an instance of the injectable.\nThe factory can call <code>inject</code> to access the <code><a href=\"api/core/Injector\" class=\"code-anchor\">Injector</a></code> and request injection of dependencies.</li>\n</ul>\n\n</section>\n\n\n\n  \n\n\n  </div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/core\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/core\n - api/core/Injectable#providedIn\n - api/core/InjectableType\n - api/core/Injector\n - api/core/InjectorType\n - api/core/NgModule\n - api/core/ResolvedReflectiveFactory#factory\n - api/core/Type\n - api/core/defineInjectable#defineinjectable\n - api/core/defineInjectable#description\n - https://github.com/angular/angular/edit/master/packages/core/src/di/defs.ts?message=docs(core)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...#L111-L136\n - https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/7.0.0/packages/core/src/di/defs.ts#L111-L136\n-->"
